TITLE: Implementing Custom Shape Props Migrations in tldraw
DESCRIPTION: Defines migrations for custom shape properties using createShapePropsMigrationSequence, allowing shape data to evolve over time with proper backwards compatibility.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tldraw/tldraw/blob/main/apps/docs/content/docs/persistence.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
import { createShapePropsMigrationSequence, createShapePropsMigrationIds, ShapeUtil } from 'tldraw'

// Migrations must start a 1 and be sequential integers.
const Versions = createShapePropMigrationIds('custom-shape', {
	AddColor: 1,
})

class MyCustomShapeUtil extends ShapeUtil {
	static type = 'custom-shape'
	static migrations = createShapePropsMigrationSequence({
		sequence: [
			{
				id: Versions.AddColor,
				up(props) {
					// set the default color
					props.color = 'black'
				},
			},
		],
	})

	// ...
}
```

